{"tha-ap344:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap344:0.2":"Ekapadumiyavagga ","tha-ap344:0.3":"2 Tinuppalamaliyattheraapadana ","tha-ap344:1.1":"“Candabhaganaditire, ","tha-ap344:1.2":"ahosim vanaro tada; ","tha-ap344:1.3":"Addasam virajam buddham, ","tha-ap344:1.4":"nisinnam pabbatantare. ","tha-ap344:2.1":"Obhasentam disa sabba, ","tha-ap344:2.2":"salarajamva phullitam; ","tha-ap344:2.3":"Lakkhanabyanjanupetam, ","tha-ap344:2.4":"disva attamano ahum. ","tha-ap344:3.1":"Udaggacitto sumano, ","tha-ap344:3.2":"pitiya hatthamanaso; ","tha-ap344:3.3":"Tini uppalapupphani, ","tha-ap344:3.4":"matthake abhiropayim. ","tha-ap344:4.1":"Pupphani abhiropetva, ","tha-ap344:4.2":"vipassissa mahesino; ","tha-ap344:4.3":"Sagaravo bhavitvana, ","tha-ap344:4.4":"pakkamim uttaramukho. ","tha-ap344:5.1":"Gacchanto patikutiko, ","tha-ap344:5.2":"vippasannena cetasa; ","tha-ap344:5.3":"Selantare patitvana, ","tha-ap344:5.4":"papunim jivitakkhayam. ","tha-ap344:6.1":"Tena kammena sukatena, ","tha-ap344:6.2":"cetanapanidhihi ca; ","tha-ap344:6.3":"Jahitva manusam deham, ","tha-ap344:6.4":"tavatimsamagacchaham. ","tha-ap344:7.1":"Satanam tinikkhattunca, ","tha-ap344:7.2":"devarajjam akarayim; ","tha-ap344:7.3":"Satanam pancakkhattunca, ","tha-ap344:7.4":"cakkavatti ahosaham. ","tha-ap344:8.1":"Ekanavutito kappe, ","tha-ap344:8.2":"yam pupphamabhipujayim; ","tha-ap344:8.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap344:8.4":"buddhapujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap344:9.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap344:9.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap344:9.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap344:10.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma tinuppalamaliyo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap344:11.1":"Tinuppalamaliyattherassapadanam dutiyam. "}